data.description: This home is being offered at the original price of $370,000.00. Priced to sell in the beautiful Forest Acres.   Welcome to the heart of Forest Acres, where timeless charm meets modern comfort in this 3-bedroom, 1.5-bath haven. Inside, you'll discover the elegance of gleaming oak hardwood floors, a kitchen revamped with granite countertops for culinary adventures, and tech upgrades including a brand new tankless water heater, updated HVAC, and ionizing ductwork for a breath of fresh air. Best of all, there is a Florida room enveloped in large windows and enhanced with built-in bookshelves that you will never want to leave.  Step into the outdoors and unwind in your private sanctuary – a lush yard surrounded by mature landscaping, a generous half-acre backyard enclosed by a privacy fence, and solar panels contributing to eco-friendly living. Embrace the serenity of the woods while enjoying the proximity to city life.  Extra perks include residing in the premier school district, soaking up the community spirit in sought-after Forest Acres, and a freshly painted exterior ensuring a sharp and well-maintained curb appeal.  This Forest Acres gem isn't just a house; it's a welcoming retreat ready for you to call home. Schedule a visit and make it yours today!
